Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在传说终年冰雪不化的地方 斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆他们遇到了班图族的少女敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是班图族似乎被伊鲁贝克率领的 鬼骑士军团控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 巴隆在和伊鲁贝克的战斗中受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯他们也被驱使到洞窟里干活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪山中进行的可怕阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的核心竟是能治愈受重伤的鬼骑士的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:11.38,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,253)}激战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:11.38,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(343,388)}魔之山脊 -后篇-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆阁下 巴隆阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你恢复意识了吗 巴隆阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用高兴成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到居然会在这种雪山重逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我偶然发现 你可能会就那样流着血被冻死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又受你关照了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 居然被奇怪的鬼手袭击落到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击你的恐怕是鬼骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是德罗斯特国的秘密军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由从阿拉德大陆的各地 聚集而来的鬼剑士组成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说最近鬼骑士在斯顿雪域 似乎有图谋不轨的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是接到教团的命令而来这一带调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种偏僻的深山 那伙人到底想干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说鬼剑士们得到了产生鬼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我快点干 不然饶不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那些混账
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要压榨我们到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这只手告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的鬼手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是我来到军队之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是观光的古迹还是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能有这么大的功效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样继续进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要用这种力量 改变大陆目前的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次得到的资料我这就送到本国的研究所去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被治愈的人 也马上送他们回国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族的家伙要怎么处置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的饭量可真是不容小觑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保守秘密 最好的办法就是灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就顺便把那个相亲相爱的Party也灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给你们善后了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆阁下 你的伤还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心他们会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种性格还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有工夫舒服的躺着还不如起来干活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都在干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙该搬的东西还没搬完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就连他的份一起搬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 卡本西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你没什么好说的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽梅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面可真凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再干下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 差不多该逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的体力 似乎也都到极限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把班图族的人一起带出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡贝俏 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 你们居然在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 我一打暗号你们就冲出箱子制造骚乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.23,0:08:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去把我的武器拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 大家 一定要保护好老人和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是要烧的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把下一个搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克爆弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以尽情的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负我的是哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族是自尊心很强的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会对鬼骑士卑颜屈膝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是族长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时候才更该统率大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那个世界后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:12:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 这花还有这样的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧死你 啊热热热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么啊 那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 巴隆 还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也在 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这东西 在往上升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 不能让它到地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西和白子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西到了地面上就会引起卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯 阻止它的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 把大家带到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能失去那个花 别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前承蒙你关照了啊 要好好返还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 鬼手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个手和你的手不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说要让它停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 烧了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没有注意到这个事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 卡贝俏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖花 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来和你玩玩 笨枪手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是纽梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚大人 从这走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把毫无关系的班图族也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做大事多少都要有一些牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便决定别人的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快结束战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们都打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不是冲着你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙被打到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正是恶有恶报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做伊鲁贝克 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆·阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记住这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是会很快就忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都救出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意 卡鲁松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚做的也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些家伙完全打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们借助那花的力量治好了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那力量是我们无法触碰的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片大陆至今还被诅咒着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那个卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,族人能得救全托你们的福 不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们班图族也是勇敢的一族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局圆满真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还在装什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 就算是我也不是不死之身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 人家可是一直在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子在担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵啦你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你要去什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在来这的路上发现了一个很不错的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想是不是要好好泡下保养下皮肤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对治愈伤口有好处的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去 要去 马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我一个人的秘密哦 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们也没什么吧
